{
  "video_id": "q1sk47FLAmg",
  "title": "Chris Gerdes: The future race car -- 150mph, and no driver",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Morton Bast Reviewer: Thu-Huong Ha"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15766.0,
      "end_time": 17173.0,
      "text": "So, how many of you have ever"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17173.0,
      "end_time": 18828.0,
      "text": "gotten behind the wheel of a car"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18828.0,
      "end_time": 24515.0,
      "text": "when you really shouldn&#39;t have been driving?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24515.0,
      "end_time": 26420.0,
      "text": "Maybe you&#39;re out on the road for a long day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26420.0,
      "end_time": 27910.0,
      "text": "and you just wanted to get home."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27910.0,
      "end_time": 30557.0,
      "text": "You were tired, but you felt you could drive a few more miles."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30557.0,
      "end_time": 31756.0,
      "text": "Maybe you thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 31756.0,
      "end_time": 33773.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve had less to drink than everybody else,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 33773.0,
      "end_time": 35509.0,
      "text": "I should be the one to go home."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 35509.0,
      "end_time": 40100.0,
      "text": "Or maybe your mind was just entirely elsewhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40100.0,
      "end_time": 41554.0,
      "text": "Does this sound familiar to you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41554.0,
      "end_time": 44452.0,
      "text": "Now, in those situations, wouldn&#39;t it be great"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44452.0,
      "end_time": 46450.0,
      "text": "if there was a button on your dashboard"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 46450.0,
      "end_time": 52388.0,
      "text": "that you could push, and the car would get you home safely?"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52388.0,
      "end_time": 54681.0,
      "text": "Now, that&#39;s been the promise of the self-driving car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54681.0,
      "end_time": 57308.0,
      "text": "the autonomous vehicle, and it&#39;s been the dream"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 57308.0,
      "end_time": 60557.0,
      "text": "since at least 1939, when General Motors showcased"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 60557.0,
      "end_time": 63859.0,
      "text": "this idea at their Futurama booth at the World&#39;s Fair."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 63859.0,
      "end_time": 65802.0,
      "text": "Now, it&#39;s been one of those dreams"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65802.0,
      "end_time": 70160.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s always seemed about 20 years in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 70160.0,
      "end_time": 72699.0,
      "text": "Now, two weeks ago, that dream took a step forward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 72699.0,
      "end_time": 75964.0,
      "text": "when the state of Nevada granted Google&#39;s self-driving car"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 75964.0,
      "end_time": 79564.0,
      "text": "the very first license for an autonomous vehicle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 79564.0,
      "end_time": 81809.0,
      "text": "clearly establishing that it&#39;s legal for them"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 81809.0,
      "end_time": 83619.0,
      "text": "to test it on the roads in Nevada."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 83619.0,
      "end_time": 87346.0,
      "text": "Now, California&#39;s considering similar legislation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 87346.0,
      "end_time": 89754.0,
      "text": "and this would make sure that the autonomous car"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 89754.0,
      "end_time": 92731.0,
      "text": "is not one of those things that has to stay in Vegas."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 92731.0,
      "end_time": 94827.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 94827.0,
      "end_time": 98611.0,
      "text": "Now, in my lab at Stanford, we&#39;ve been working on"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 98611.0,
      "end_time": 102980.0,
      "text": "autonomous cars too, but with a slightly different spin"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 102980.0,
      "end_time": 106346.0,
      "text": "on things. You see, we&#39;ve been developing robotic race cars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 106346.0,
      "end_time": 110466.0,
      "text": "cars that can actually push themselves to the very limits"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 110466.0,
      "end_time": 112705.0,
      "text": "of physical performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 112706.0,
      "end_time": 115319.0,
      "text": "Now, why would we want to do such a thing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 115319.0,
      "end_time": 117419.0,
      "text": "Well, there&#39;s two really good reasons for this."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 117419.0,
      "end_time": 121378.0,
      "text": "First, we believe that before people turn over control"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 121378.0,
      "end_time": 124212.0,
      "text": "to an autonomous car, that autonomous car should be"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 124212.0,
      "end_time": 127466.0,
      "text": "at least as good as the very best human drivers."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 127466.0,
      "end_time": 130770.0,
      "text": "Now, if you&#39;re like me, and the other 70 percent of the population"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 130770.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132964.0,
      "text": "who know that we are above-average drivers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 132964.0,
      "end_time": 136139.0,
      "text": "you understand that&#39;s a very high bar."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 136139.0,
      "end_time": 138531.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s another reason as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 138531.0,
      "end_time": 142107.0,
      "text": "Just like race car drivers can use all of the friction"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 142107.0,
      "end_time": 143387.0,
      "text": "between the tire and the road,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 143387.0,
      "end_time": 146564.0,
      "text": "all of the car&#39;s capabilities to go as fast as possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 146564.0,
      "end_time": 149909.0,
      "text": "we want to use all of those capabilities to avoid"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 149909.0,
      "end_time": 151497.0,
      "text": "any accident we can."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 151497.0,
      "end_time": 153547.0,
      "text": "Now, you may push the car to the limits"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 153547.0,
      "end_time": 155514.0,
      "text": "not because you&#39;re driving too fast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 155514.0,
      "end_time": 157674.0,
      "text": "but because you&#39;ve hit an icy patch of road,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 157674.0,
      "end_time": 159378.0,
      "text": "conditions have changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 159378.0,
      "end_time": 162138.0,
      "text": "In those situations, we want a car"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 162139.0,
      "end_time": 165859.0,
      "text": "that is capable enough to avoid any accident"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 165859.0,
      "end_time": 168537.0,
      "text": "that can physically be avoided."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 168537.0,
      "end_time": 172804.0,
      "text": "I must confess, there&#39;s kind of a third motivation as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 172804.0,
      "end_time": 175600.0,
      "text": "You see, I have a passion for racing."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 175600.0,
      "end_time": 177824.0,
      "text": "In the past, I&#39;ve been a race car owner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 177824.0,
      "end_time": 180379.0,
      "text": "a crew chief and a driving coach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 180379.0,
      "end_time": 184233.0,
      "text": "although maybe not at the level that you&#39;re currently expecting."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 184234.0,
      "end_time": 186938.0,
      "text": "One of the things that we&#39;ve developed in the lab --"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 186938.0,
      "end_time": 188642.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve developed several vehicles --"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 188642.0,
      "end_time": 190877.0,
      "text": "is what we believe is the world&#39;s first"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 190877.0,
      "end_time": 193242.0,
      "text": "autonomously drifting car."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 193242.0,
      "end_time": 195755.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s another one of those categories"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 195755.0,
      "end_time": 198178.0,
      "text": "where maybe there&#39;s not a lot of competition."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 198178.0,
      "end_time": 199585.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 199586.0,
      "end_time": 203408.0,
      "text": "But this is P1. It&#39;s an entirely student-built electric vehicle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 203408.0,
      "end_time": 205486.0,
      "text": "which through using its rear-wheel drive"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 205486.0,
      "end_time": 207510.0,
      "text": "and front-wheel steer-by-wire"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 207510.0,
      "end_time": 209118.0,
      "text": "can drift around corners."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 209118.0,
      "end_time": 211317.0,
      "text": "It can get sideways like a rally car driver,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 211318.0,
      "end_time": 213330.0,
      "text": "always able to take the tightest curve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 213330.0,
      "end_time": 216337.0,
      "text": "even on slippery, changing surfaces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 216337.0,
      "end_time": 217953.0,
      "text": "never spinning out."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 217953.0,
      "end_time": 220321.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve also worked with Volkswagen Oracle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 220321.0,
      "end_time": 223745.0,
      "text": "on Shelley, an autonomous race car that has raced"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 223745.0,
      "end_time": 226815.0,
      "text": "at 150 miles an hour through the Bonneville Salt Flats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 226815.0,
      "end_time": 231286.0,
      "text": "gone around Thunderhill Raceway Park in the sun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 231286.0,
      "end_time": 233925.0,
      "text": "the wind and the rain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 233925.0,
      "end_time": 238943.0,
      "text": "and navigated the 153 turns and 12.4 miles"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 238943.0,
      "end_time": 240505.0,
      "text": "of the Pikes Peak Hill Climb route"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 240505.0,
      "end_time": 243978.0,
      "text": "in Colorado with nobody at the wheel."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 243978.0,
      "end_time": 245426.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 245426.0,
      "end_time": 250992.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 250992.0,
      "end_time": 254271.0,
      "text": "I guess it goes without saying that we&#39;ve had a lot of fun"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 254271.0,
      "end_time": 255575.0,
      "text": "doing this."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 255575.0,
      "end_time": 259231.0,
      "text": "But in fact, there&#39;s something else that we&#39;ve developed"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 259232.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262287.0,
      "text": "in the process of developing these autonomous cars."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 262287.0,
      "end_time": 266157.0,
      "text": "We have developed a tremendous appreciation"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 266158.0,
      "end_time": 269975.0,
      "text": "for the capabilities of human race car drivers."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 269975.0,
      "end_time": 274320.0,
      "text": "As we&#39;ve looked at the question of how well do these cars perform,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 274320.0,
      "end_time": 277599.0,
      "text": "we wanted to compare them to our human counterparts."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 277599.0,
      "end_time": 283279.0,
      "text": "And we discovered their human counterparts are amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 283279.0,
      "end_time": 287302.0,
      "text": "Now, we can take a map of a race track,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 287302.0,
      "end_time": 289672.0,
      "text": "we can take a mathematical model of a car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 289672.0,
      "end_time": 292575.0,
      "text": "and with some iteration, we can actually find"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 292575.0,
      "end_time": 294200.0,
      "text": "the fastest way around that track."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 294200.0,
      "end_time": 296733.0,
      "text": "We line that up with data that we record"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 296733.0,
      "end_time": 298166.0,
      "text": "from a professional driver,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 298166.0,
      "end_time": 302273.0,
      "text": "and the resemblance is absolutely remarkable."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 302273.0,
      "end_time": 305485.0,
      "text": "Yes, there are subtle differences here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 305485.0,
      "end_time": 308612.0,
      "text": "but the human race car driver is able to go out"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 308612.0,
      "end_time": 310947.0,
      "text": "and drive an amazingly fast line,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 310947.0,
      "end_time": 313277.0,
      "text": "without the benefit of an algorithm that compares"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 313277.0,
      "end_time": 315885.0,
      "text": "the trade-off between going as fast as possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 315885.0,
      "end_time": 317921.0,
      "text": "in this corner, and shaving a little bit of time"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 317922.0,
      "end_time": 319824.0,
      "text": "off of the straight over here."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 319824.0,
      "end_time": 323281.0,
      "text": "Not only that, they&#39;re able to do it lap"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 323281.0,
      "end_time": 325656.0,
      "text": "after lap after lap."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 325656.0,
      "end_time": 328568.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re able to go out and consistently do this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 328568.0,
      "end_time": 332695.0,
      "text": "pushing the car to the limits every single time."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 332696.0,
      "end_time": 335865.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s extraordinary to watch."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 335865.0,
      "end_time": 337931.0,
      "text": "You put them in a new car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 337931.0,
      "end_time": 341832.0,
      "text": "and after a few laps, they&#39;ve found the fastest line in that car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 341833.0,
      "end_time": 345710.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re off to the races."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 345710.0,
      "end_time": 346856.0,
      "text": "It really makes you think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 346856.0,
      "end_time": 351727.0,
      "text": "we&#39;d love to know what&#39;s going on inside their brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 351727.0,
      "end_time": 356268.0,
      "text": "So as researchers, that&#39;s what we decided to find out."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 356268.0,
      "end_time": 358800.0,
      "text": "We decided to instrument not only the car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 358800.0,
      "end_time": 360575.0,
      "text": "but also the race car driver,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 360575.0,
      "end_time": 363344.0,
      "text": "to try to get a glimpse into what was going on"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 363344.0,
      "end_time": 365530.0,
      "text": "in their head as they were doing this."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 365530.0,
      "end_time": 369479.0,
      "text": "Now, this is Dr. Lene Harbott applying electrodes"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 369480.0,
      "end_time": 370712.0,
      "text": "to the head of John Morton."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 370712.0,
      "end_time": 373700.0,
      "text": "John Morton is a former Can-Am and IMSA driver,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 373701.0,
      "end_time": 375501.0,
      "text": "who&#39;s also a class champion at Le Mans."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 375501.0,
      "end_time": 378996.0,
      "text": "Fantastic driver, and very willing to put up with graduate students"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 378997.0,
      "end_time": 380852.0,
      "text": "and this sort of research."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 380852.0,
      "end_time": 383524.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s putting electrodes on his head"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 383524.0,
      "end_time": 385636.0,
      "text": "so that we can monitor the electrical activity"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 385636.0,
      "end_time": 388468.0,
      "text": "in John&#39;s brain as he races around the track."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 388468.0,
      "end_time": 391663.0,
      "text": "Now, clearly we&#39;re not going to put a couple of electrodes on his head"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 391663.0,
      "end_time": 394933.0,
      "text": "and understand exactly what all of his thoughts are on the track."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 394933.0,
      "end_time": 398340.0,
      "text": "However, neuroscientists have identified certain patterns"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 398340.0,
      "end_time": 402101.0,
      "text": "that let us tease out some very important aspects of this."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 402101.0,
      "end_time": 403948.0,
      "text": "For instance, the resting brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 403948.0,
      "end_time": 406102.0,
      "text": "tends to generate a lot of alpha waves."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 406103.0,
      "end_time": 409855.0,
      "text": "In contrast, theta waves are associated with"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 409855.0,
      "end_time": 413390.0,
      "text": "a lot of cognitive activity, like visual processing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 413390.0,
      "end_time": 416870.0,
      "text": "things where the driver is thinking quite a bit."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 416870.0,
      "end_time": 417750.0,
      "text": "Now, we can measure this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 417750.0,
      "end_time": 419735.0,
      "text": "and we can look at the relative power"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 419735.0,
      "end_time": 421935.0,
      "text": "between the theta waves and the alpha waves."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 421935.0,
      "end_time": 424377.0,
      "text": "This gives us a measure of mental workload,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 424377.0,
      "end_time": 427944.0,
      "text": "how much the driver is actually challenged cognitively"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 427944.0,
      "end_time": 429730.0,
      "text": "at any point along the track."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 429730.0,
      "end_time": 432672.0,
      "text": "Now, we wanted to see if we could actually record this"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 432672.0,
      "end_time": 435710.0,
      "text": "on the track, so we headed down south to Laguna Seca."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 435710.0,
      "end_time": 437726.0,
      "text": "Laguna Seca is a legendary raceway"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 437726.0,
      "end_time": 440270.0,
      "text": "about halfway between Salinas and Monterey."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 440270.0,
      "end_time": 442114.0,
      "text": "It has a curve there called the Corkscrew."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 442114.0,
      "end_time": 444830.0,
      "text": "Now, the Corkscrew is a chicane, followed by a quick"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 444831.0,
      "end_time": 447577.0,
      "text": "right-handed turn as the road drops three stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 447577.0,
      "end_time": 451343.0,
      "text": "Now, the strategy for driving this as explained to me was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 451343.0,
      "end_time": 453365.0,
      "text": "you aim for the bush in the distance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 453365.0,
      "end_time": 456390.0,
      "text": "and as the road falls away, you realize it was actually the top of a tree."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 456390.0,
      "end_time": 459693.0,
      "text": "All right, so thanks to the Revs Program at Stanford,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 459694.0,
      "end_time": 461167.0,
      "text": "we were able to take John there"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 461167.0,
      "end_time": 462131.0,
      "text": "and put him behind the wheel"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 462131.0,
      "end_time": 464570.0,
      "text": "of a 1960 Porsche Abarth Carrera."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 464570.0,
      "end_time": 468268.0,
      "text": "Life is way too short for boring cars."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 468268.0,
      "end_time": 470270.0,
      "text": "So, here you see John on the track,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 470270.0,
      "end_time": 472211.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s going up the hill -- Oh! Somebody liked that --"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 472211.0,
      "end_time": 474676.0,
      "text": "and you can see, actually, his mental workload"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 474676.0,
      "end_time": 476829.0,
      "text": "-- measuring here in the red bar --"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 476829.0,
      "end_time": 479172.0,
      "text": "you can see his actions as he approaches."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 479172.0,
      "end_time": 482402.0,
      "text": "Now watch, he has to downshift."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 482402.0,
      "end_time": 483163.0,
      "text": "And then he has to turn left."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 483163.0,
      "end_time": 487156.0,
      "text": "Look for the tree, and down."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 487156.0,
      "end_time": 489994.0,
      "text": "Not surprisingly, you can see this is a pretty challenging task."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 489994.0,
      "end_time": 492970.0,
      "text": "You can see his mental workload spike as he goes through this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 492970.0,
      "end_time": 495340.0,
      "text": "as you would expect with something that requires"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 495340.0,
      "end_time": 497843.0,
      "text": "this level of complexity."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 497843.0,
      "end_time": 501259.0,
      "text": "But what&#39;s really interesting is to look at areas of the track"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 501259.0,
      "end_time": 504105.0,
      "text": "where his mental workload doesn&#39;t increase."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 504105.0,
      "end_time": 505600.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to take you around now"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 505600.0,
      "end_time": 506689.0,
      "text": "to the other side of the track."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 506689.0,
      "end_time": 509250.0,
      "text": "Turn three. And John&#39;s going to go into that corner"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 509250.0,
      "end_time": 511575.0,
      "text": "and the rear end of the car is going to begin to slide out."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 511576.0,
      "end_time": 513593.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s going to have to correct for that with steering."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 513592.0,
      "end_time": 515823.0,
      "text": "So watch as John does this here."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 515823.0,
      "end_time": 518145.0,
      "text": "Watch the mental workload, and watch the steering."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 518145.0,
      "end_time": 521818.0,
      "text": "The car begins to slide out, dramatic maneuver to correct it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 521818.0,
      "end_time": 525341.0,
      "text": "and no change whatsoever in the mental workload."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 525341.0,
      "end_time": 528173.0,
      "text": "Not a challenging task."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 528173.0,
      "end_time": 531373.0,
      "text": "In fact, entirely reflexive."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 531373.0,
      "end_time": 535160.0,
      "text": "Now, our data processing on this is still preliminary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 535160.0,
      "end_time": 537688.0,
      "text": "but it really seems that these phenomenal feats"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 537688.0,
      "end_time": 539298.0,
      "text": "that the race car drivers are performing"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 539298.0,
      "end_time": 541208.0,
      "text": "are instinctive."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 541208.0,
      "end_time": 544598.0,
      "text": "They are things that they have simply learned to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 544598.0,
      "end_time": 546880.0,
      "text": "It requires very little mental workload"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 546880.0,
      "end_time": 549704.0,
      "text": "for them to perform these amazing feats."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 549704.0,
      "end_time": 552839.0,
      "text": "And their actions are fantastic."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 552839.0,
      "end_time": 555450.0,
      "text": "This is exactly what you want to do on the steering wheel"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 555450.0,
      "end_time": 558787.0,
      "text": "to catch the car in this situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 558787.0,
      "end_time": 562232.0,
      "text": "Now, this has given us tremendous insight"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 562232.0,
      "end_time": 565353.0,
      "text": "and inspiration for our own autonomous vehicles."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 565354.0,
      "end_time": 567282.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve started to ask the question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 567282.0,
      "end_time": 569535.0,
      "text": "Can we make them a little less algorithmic"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 569535.0,
      "end_time": 571983.0,
      "text": "and a little more intuitive?"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 571984.0,
      "end_time": 574265.0,
      "text": "Can we take this reflexive action"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 574265.0,
      "end_time": 576552.0,
      "text": "that we see from the very best race car drivers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 576552.0,
      "end_time": 578201.0,
      "text": "introduce it to our cars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 578201.0,
      "end_time": 580185.0,
      "text": "and maybe even into a system that could"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 580185.0,
      "end_time": 582152.0,
      "text": "get onto your car in the future?"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 582153.0,
      "end_time": 583764.0,
      "text": "That would take us a long step"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 583764.0,
      "end_time": 586273.0,
      "text": "along the road to autonomous vehicles"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 586273.0,
      "end_time": 588185.0,
      "text": "that drive as well as the best humans."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 588185.0,
      "end_time": 591625.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s made us think a little bit more deeply as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 591625.0,
      "end_time": 594593.0,
      "text": "Do we want something more from our car"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 594593.0,
      "end_time": 596433.0,
      "text": "than to simply be a chauffeur?"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 596433.0,
      "end_time": 600668.0,
      "text": "Do we want our car to perhaps be a partner, a coach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 600668.0,
      "end_time": 603755.0,
      "text": "someone that can use their understanding of the situation"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 603755.0,
      "end_time": 608110.0,
      "text": "to help us reach our potential?"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 608110.0,
      "end_time": 610284.0,
      "text": "Can, in fact, the technology not simply replace humans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 610284.0,
      "end_time": 614859.0,
      "text": "but allow us to reach the level of reflex and intuition"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 614859.0,
      "end_time": 618284.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;re all capable of?"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 618284.0,
      "end_time": 620207.0,
      "text": "So, as we move forward into this technological future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 620207.0,
      "end_time": 623280.0,
      "text": "I want you to just pause and think of that for a moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 623280.0,
      "end_time": 626803.0,
      "text": "What is the ideal balance of human and machine?"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 626803.0,
      "end_time": 628512.0,
      "text": "And as we think about that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 628512.0,
      "end_time": 630242.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s take inspiration"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 630243.0,
      "end_time": 633572.0,
      "text": "from the absolutely amazing capabilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 633572.0,
      "end_time": 636388.0,
      "text": "of the human body and the human mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 636388.0,
      "end_time": 638124.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 638124.0,
      "end_time": 642728.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}